Welcome to the Sparky Skype Server Installer
============================================

This package will install:
+ SkypeSparkyServer -- listens for Skype 
	text messages to control the Irobot
	Create and relays these messages to
	controld
+ controld -- daemon that controls Irobot
	Create
+ shell_check_sparky_irobot.php -- check
	script to make sure controld 
	is started and running
+ crontab -- cron entry to schedule
	shell_check_sparky_irobot.php
	to run every minute
